          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              href="https://www.rfsl.se"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer">RFSL Sweden (internationaal)</a
            > — LHBTIQ+ hulp
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              href="https://www.unhcr.org"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer">UNHCR</a
